{"id":1194,"date":"2024-08-03T18:11:18","date_gmt":"2024-08-03T18:11:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1194"},"modified":"2024-08-03T18:11:18","modified_gmt":"2024-08-03T18:11:18","slug":"mission-010","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-010\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #010: As Hard as They Come"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Mission #010: As Hard as They Come<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Gurun Town, house in plaza northwest of Regi statue \u2013 Rancher in the living room<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Completed main story missions up until Gurun Town<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Collect 20 Hard Stones<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>TM111 Smack Down<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>A Rancher in Gurun Town wants you to bring him 20 Hard Stones. He\u2019ll give you TM111 Smack Down in exchange.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to Gurun Town and head to the house just north of the Pok\u00e9mon Center, on the northwest corner of the Regi statue plaza.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/010\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-house-in-gurun-town.jpg\" alt=\"The house in Gurun Town \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The house in Gurun Town<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/010\/02-pokemon-unbound-this-man-requests-a-lot-of-hard-stones.jpg\" alt=\"This man requests a lot of Hard Stones \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>This man requests a lot of Hard Stones<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Rancher in the living room wants you to collect 20 Hard Stones and bring them to him.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/010\/03-pokemon-unbound-kbt-expressway-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"KBT Expressway Entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>KBT Expressway Entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>There are two main repeatable sources of Hard Stones. <\/p>\n<p>Digging is the first and probably the most reliable of these methods.<\/p>\n<p>Before you beat the Pok\u00e9mon League, the only place to do this is in the <strong>Crater Town section of the KBT Expressway<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/010\/04-pokemon-unbound-you-can-pay-to-mine-in-this-section.jpg\" alt=\"You can pay to mine in this section \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>You can pay to mine in this section<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Walk north into the tunnel and you\u2019ll eventually see a Worker who will charge you P1000 to use his tools.<\/p>\n<p>The key is to break as much of the rock using the hammer and pick tools before the wall collapses. The crack in the top of the interface will grow with every hit, so be careful.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/010\/05-pokemon-unbound-the-mining-minigame.jpg\" alt=\"The mining minigame - Hard Stones are the 2x2 grey octagonal gemstone pictured \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The mining minigame &#8211; Hard Stones are the 2&#215;2 grey octagonal gemstone pictured<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>If you\u2019re lucky, you can uncover Hard Stones, Heart Scales, Everstones, Revives, any of the evolution Stones, and a few more assorted goodies.<\/p>\n<p>Hard Stones are one of the more common items you can get, and they look like grey octagonal gemstones.<\/p>\n<h3>Alternative Sources<\/h3>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/010\/06-pokemon-unbound-the-great-desert-is-the-other-source.jpg\" alt=\"The Great Desert is the other source \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Great Desert is the other source<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The other place where you can get Hard Stones is the Great Desert. <\/p>\n<p>Breaking rocks with Rock Smash here will sometimes get you items and Fossils.<\/p>\n<p>Hard Stones are one of the more common drops from the smashed rocks.<\/p>\n<p>When you return to the Rancher with the 20 Hard Stones, he\u2019ll give you TM111 Smack Down.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/010\/07-pokemon-unbound-the-rancher-is-grateful.jpg\" alt=\"The Rancher is grateful \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Rancher is grateful<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1195,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1194","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1194","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1195"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1194"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1194"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}